# Grace Config 6 - vEGM, 1 GPU per socket, 4 sockets, 36 NUMA nodes
# HostTopology: 4 sockets, 4 GpuSmmuGroups (1 GPU each), 4 EgmSocketInfos
# CpuMem nodes 0-3 (one per socket), GPU initiator nodes 4-35 (8 per GPU)
